dfischer.utils

Class LoadtestInlineScriptVar

  • java.lang.Object
    • dfischer.utils.LoadtestInlineScriptVar

  • public class LoadtestInlineScriptVar
extends java.lang.Object
    A declaration of a Java load test program variable which is passed to an inline script or is returned from an inline script.

    V5.4-F
